TITLE: URL Encoded Form with Binary Values Configuration
DESCRIPTION: YAML configuration for a form that includes binary data (image) using the byte format. The encoding object specifies the content types for the binary data.
SOURCE: https://github.com/oai/openapi-specification/blob/main/versions/3.0.4.md#2025-04-18_snippet_44

LANGUAGE: yaml
CODE:
```
requestBody:
  content:
    application/x-www-form-urlencoded:
      schema:
        type: object
        properties:
          name:
            type: string
          icon:
            # The default with "format: byte" is application/octet-stream,
            # so we need to set image media type(s) in the Encoding Object.
            type: string
            format: byte
  encoding:
    icon:
      contentType: image/png, image/jpeg
```

